languages.text: "Вся эта история вокруг нашего нового Главного технопровидца заставляет меня нервничать... словно огромный механизм пришел в движение, стремясь свести свои части воедино".
"The whole story surrounding our new Enginseer Prime makes me antsy... It's like a huge machine has been set into motion, and it can't wait to fit all its parts together."

languages.text: “我们新任引擎先知身边的那些故事让我感到相当不安……给我的感觉就像是巨大的机器已经启动，迫不及待想把所有零件组装在一起。”
languages.original_text: "The whole story surrounding our new Enginseer Prime makes me antsy... It's like a huge machine has been set into motion, and it can't wait to fit all its parts together."

traits.locale_text: “我们新任引擎先知身边的那些故事让我感到相当不安……它给我的感觉就像，巨大的机器已经启动，迫不及待想把所有零件组装在一起。”
traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: « Toutes ces histoires à propos du nouveau technaugure primus me rendent nerveuse... C'est comme si une énorme machine s'était mise en marche et qu'elle avait hâte de pouvoir assembler toutes ses pièces. »
languages.original_text: "The whole story surrounding our new Enginseer Prime makes me antsy... It's like a huge machine has been set into motion, and it can't wait to fit all its parts together."

traits.locale_text: « Toutes ces histoires à propos du nouveau technaugure en chef me rendent nerveuse... C'est comme si une énorme machine s'était mise en marche et qu'elle avait hâte de pouvoir assembler toutes ses pièces. »
traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: «La historia que rodea a nuestro nuevo visioingeniero primero me pone de los nervios... Es como si una enorme máquina hubiera entrado en funcionamiento y quisiera conectar sus piezas cuanto antes».
languages.original_text: "The whole story surrounding our new Enginseer Prime makes me antsy... It's like a huge machine has been set into motion, and it can't wait to fit all its parts together."

traits.locale_text: «La historia que rodea a nuestro nuevo visioingeniero jefe me pone de los nervios... Es como si una enorme máquina hubiera entrado en funcionamiento y quisiera conectar sus piezas cuanto antes».
traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: 「新しい主任旗艦整備師がいるフロアは落ち着かないわ…巨大な機械を稼働して、すべてのパーツを取り付けるのが待ちきれないみたい」
languages.original_text: "The whole story surrounding our new Enginseer Prime makes me antsy... It's like a huge machine has been set into motion, and it can't wait to fit all its parts together."

traits.locale_text: 「新しい機関整備師長がいるフロアは落ち着かないわ…巨大な機械を稼働して、すべてのパーツを取り付けるのが待ちきれないみたい」
traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: "Die ganze Geschichte um unseren neuen Maschinenseher Primus macht mich unruhig ... Es ist, als sei eine riesige Maschine in Gang gesetzt worden und könne nicht darauf warten, alle ihre Teile zusammenzusetzen."
languages.original_text: "The whole story surrounding our new Enginseer Prime makes me antsy... It's like a huge machine has been set into motion, and it can't wait to fit all its parts together."

traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion
